==Ivor Novello Awards==
The [[Ivor Novello Awards]] are presented annually in London by the British Academy of Composers and Songwriters. Radiohead have received one award.<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2008-10-23|url=http://www.nme.com/news/amy-winehouse/36815|title=Amy Winehouse gets dad to pick up Ivor Novello award|work=NME|date=2008-05-22}}</ref>

